{
  "texts": [
    "The rest of her cranial nerve examination was unremarkable.",
    "Slit lamp examination was remarkable only for mild nuclear sclerosis OU.",
    "Dilated fundus examination showed mild, diffuse optic disc swelling OD and normal disc OS with normal maculae, vessels, and periphery.",
    "Humphrey SITA Standard visual field with size V stimulus showed a dense central scotoma in the right eye and was normal for the left eye using the size III stimulus.",
    "OCT showed mild, diffuse retinal nerve fiber layer thickening OD and normal OS."
  ]
}